WEBVTT

00:00:00.910 --> 00:00:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[line ringing]</b></Default>

00:00:06.620 --> 00:00:08.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>FIND TOUKO KIRISHIMA
MAI-SAN IS IN DANGER!</b></Default>

00:00:08.910 --> 00:00:09.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[clicks]</b></Default>

00:00:09.910 --> 00:00:12.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[AUTOMATED VOICE] {\i1}Connecting{\i0}
{\i1}to voicemail service.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:00:12.910 --> 00:00:15.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Please leave your message{\i0}
{\i1}after the beep.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:00:15.949 --> 00:00:17.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[beep]</b></Default>

00:00:17.579 --> 00:00:18.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, hello.</b></Default>

00:00:18.660 --> 00:00:19.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm calling to confirm</b></Default>

00:00:19.870 --> 00:00:22.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if this number belongs to
Miss Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:00:22.829 --> 00:00:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] So, what did you say
in your message?</b></Default>

00:00:25.829 --> 00:00:27.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just said</b></Default>

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:31.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because I wanted to know
how I can become Santa Claus."</b></Default>

00:00:31.250 --> 00:00:33.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If she really is
the actual Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

00:00:34.039 --> 00:00:36.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I assumed I could ask her
about what she thought.</b></Default>

00:00:37.409 --> 00:00:39.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Considering the message
Ikumi Akagi received</b></Default>

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:42.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there are two branches
of possibilities</b></Default>

00:00:42.250 --> 00:00:43.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in this scenario.</b></Default>

00:00:43.750 --> 00:00:46.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The first being that
Touko Kirishima will somehow</b></Default>

00:00:46.789 --> 00:00:49.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>directly cause physical harm
to Sakurajima.</b></Default>

00:00:49.409 --> 00:00:52.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think she'd actually
do it directly though.</b></Default>

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:53.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, she's invisible.</b></Default>

00:00:53.619 --> 00:00:56.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She would have had plenty
of chances to do it by now.</b></Default>

00:00:56.869 --> 00:00:58.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then it would be
the other possibility.</b></Default>

00:00:59.039 --> 00:01:02.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In that case, it'll likely be
someone with puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:01:02.079 --> 00:01:04.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>whose onset was
thanks to Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:01:04.290 --> 00:01:07.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They will likely put Sakurajima
in harm's way.</b></Default>

00:01:07.620 --> 00:01:08.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

00:01:08.620 --> 00:01:09.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Futaba</b></Default>

00:01:09.659 --> 00:01:12.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you think all of these recent
cases of puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:01:12.620 --> 00:01:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>really were caused
by Touko Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:01:14.829 --> 00:01:16.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said so herself, didn't she?</b></Default>

00:01:18.500 --> 00:01:21.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So what's your deal? You just
go around in that Santa outfit</b></Default>

00:01:21.950 --> 00:01:24.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>handing out puberty syndrome
to everyone as presents?</b></Default>

00:01:24.790 --> 00:01:25.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, yeah.</b></Default>

00:01:25.829 --> 00:01:28.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Santa Claus's job is to visit
all of the nice boys and girls</b></Default>

00:01:28.909 --> 00:01:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and pass out presents to them.</b></Default>

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:33.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But all we have
to go off of is her word.</b></Default>

00:01:33.409 --> 00:01:35.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way to prove
if that's even true.</b></Default>

00:01:35.909 --> 00:01:37.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which means, at this point</b></Default>

00:01:37.500 --> 00:01:40.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's only one thing you can
do now, right, Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:01:40.579 --> 00:01:42.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs] I guess you're right.</b></Default>

00:01:42.370 --> 00:01:44.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In the end</b></Default>

00:01:44.200 --> 00:01:46.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the Miniskirt Santa
somehow.</b></Default>

00:01:47.620 --> 00:01:49.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:02:55.699 --> 00:03:01.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:03:17.699 --> 00:03:18.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}DECEMBER 1ST</b></Default>

00:03:18.870 --> 00:03:19.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[MAN] Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:21.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}SECRETS AND PROMISES</b></Default>

00:03:21.199 --> 00:03:22.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}-Have a moment?
-[SAKUTA] Sure.</b></Default>

00:03:23.039 --> 00:03:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The thing is, I'd like you
to take over the role</b></Default>

00:03:25.580 --> 00:03:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of being Himeji's tutor
starting today.</b></Default>

00:03:27.620 --> 00:03:29.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is rather sudden.</b></Default>

00:03:29.120 --> 00:03:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, she had
requested it herself.</b></Default>

00:03:31.370 --> 00:03:32.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what do you think?</b></Default>

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:34.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can do it.</b></Default>

00:03:34.539 --> 00:03:36.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's great. What a relief.</b></Default>

00:03:36.870 --> 00:03:38.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hey, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:03:39.580 --> 00:03:42.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, I'm counting on you</b></Default>

00:03:43.039 --> 00:03:45.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess I'm under your care now</b></Default>

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:48.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] It's nice
to have you aboard, Himeji.</b></Default>

00:03:49.199 --> 00:03:50.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Natsuno purring]</b></Default>

00:03:50.870 --> 00:03:52.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[muffled gasping]</b></Default>

00:03:54.620 --> 00:03:57.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathes deeply]</b></Default>

00:03:58.699 --> 00:04:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NOVEMBER 29TH</b></Default>

00:04:01.620 --> 00:04:04.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was
an awfully realistic dream.</b></Default>

00:04:05.830 --> 00:04:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Huh? Mai</b></Default>

00:04:08.080 --> 00:04:09.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has been canceled?</b></Default>

00:04:09.199 --> 00:04:12.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Yeah. I just received word
from Ryoko earlier.</b></Default>

00:04:12.199 --> 00:04:14.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That means we can go
on a date for your birthday.</b></Default>

00:04:14.789 --> 00:04:17.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Exactly. So leave your schedule
open after class.</b></Default>

00:04:17.410 --> 00:04:20.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's somewhere special
I've been wanting to take you.</b></Default>

00:04:20.329 --> 00:04:21.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Where?</b></Default>

00:04:21.500 --> 00:04:23.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll just leave the fun
for when we get there.</b></Default>

00:04:23.949 --> 00:04:24.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grumbles]</b></Default>

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[IKUMI] Azusagawa.
-[BOTH] Huh?</b></Default>

00:04:32.579 --> 00:04:33.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[IKUMI] I'm sorry.</b></Default>

00:04:33.750 --> 00:04:35.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was no good.</b></Default>

00:04:35.250 --> 00:04:36.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I see.</b></Default>

00:04:36.790 --> 00:04:38.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was thinking
I'd ask my other self</b></Default>

00:04:38.699 --> 00:04:41.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what he meant by the message
he left on you yesterday.</b></Default>

00:04:41.540 --> 00:04:44.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not sure, but I don't think
our message from over here</b></Default>

00:04:44.750 --> 00:04:46.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has reached my other self yet.</b></Default>

00:04:46.620 --> 00:04:50.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ever since we tried connecting</b></Default>

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I think it's better
if you stay that way.</b></Default>

00:04:53.329 --> 00:04:54.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That likely means</b></Default>

00:04:54.449 --> 00:04:56.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your puberty syndrome
has been cured.</b></Default>

00:04:56.579 --> 00:04:58.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you dare
feel responsible about this</b></Default>

00:04:58.750 --> 00:05:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and switch with the Akagi
over there again, okay?</b></Default>

00:05:01.329 --> 00:05:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I'll be fine.</b></Default>

00:05:03.829 --> 00:05:06.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll let you know
if anything else comes up.</b></Default>

00:05:07.250 --> 00:05:08.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>#TOUKOKIRISHIMA</b></Default>

00:05:08.199 --> 00:05:09.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KASAI] Catch you later.</b></Default>

00:05:09.540 --> 00:05:11.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]
Got something after this?</b></Default>

00:05:11.449 --> 00:05:14.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My future girlfriend candidate
is calling for me.</b></Default>

00:05:14.120 --> 00:05:15.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Another mixer, huh?</b></Default>

00:05:15.660 --> 00:05:16.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You bet.</b></Default>

00:05:16.699 --> 00:05:18.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I just know
this is my lucky day!</b></Default>

00:05:18.699 --> 00:05:21.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'll look forward to
hearing some good news.</b></Default>

00:05:21.449 --> 00:05:23.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>#TOUKOKIRISHIMA
#MAISAKURAJIMA</b></Default>

00:05:23.540 --> 00:05:25.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>TOUKO AND MAI
HAVE SIMILAR SINGING VOICES</b></Default>

00:05:25.829 --> 00:05:27.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>THEY'RE THE SAME PERSON, RIGHT?</b></Default>

00:05:27.540 --> 00:05:28.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ISN'T TOUKO ACTUALLY MAI?</b></Default>

00:05:29.540 --> 00:05:30.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:05:30.620 --> 00:05:32.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still no clues, huh?</b></Default>

00:05:33.579 --> 00:05:34.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SHONAN CRAM SCHOOL</b></Default>

00:05:34.750 --> 00:05:35.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 1ST</b></Default>

00:05:38.620 --> 00:05:40.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anything else
you don't understand?</b></Default>

00:05:40.500 --> 00:05:42.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Um, right here.</b></Default>

00:05:42.579 --> 00:05:43.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which one?</b></Default>

00:05:47.079 --> 00:05:48.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}DECEMBER 1ST</b></Default>

00:05:48.870 --> 00:05:50.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[MAN] Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:05:50.410 --> 00:05:52.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}-Have a moment?
-Sure.</b></Default>

00:05:52.660 --> 00:05:55.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The thing is, I'd like you
to take over the role</b></Default>

00:05:55.250 --> 00:05:57.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of being Himeji's tutor
starting today.</b></Default>

00:05:57.540 --> 00:05:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is rather sudden.</b></Default>

00:05:59.329 --> 00:06:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, she had
requested it herself.</b></Default>

00:06:01.579 --> 00:06:02.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think?</b></Default>

00:06:03.079 --> 00:06:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can do it.</b></Default>

00:06:04.620 --> 00:06:06.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hey, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:09.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay. I'm counting on you</b></Default>

00:06:10.620 --> 00:06:13.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess I'm under
your care now, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:06:13.660 --> 00:06:15.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's nice
to have you aboard, Himeji.</b></Default>

00:06:22.410 --> 00:06:23.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] H-Himeji!</b></Default>

00:06:24.079 --> 00:06:26.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Himeji will be joining
this class starting today.</b></Default>

00:06:26.870 --> 00:06:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nice to be here, Yamada.</b></Default>

00:06:28.579 --> 00:06:29.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You too, Yoshiwa.</b></Default>

00:06:29.870 --> 00:06:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wha... Are you for real?!</b></Default>

00:06:31.829 --> 00:06:34.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what exactly
does that mean, Yamada?</b></Default>

00:06:34.370 --> 00:06:35.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YAMADA] Huh? What do you mean?</b></Default>

00:06:36.040 --> 00:06:38.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you happy about it or not?</b></Default>

00:06:38.079 --> 00:06:40.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I don't really feel
one way or the other.</b></Default>

00:06:40.949 --> 00:06:44.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, Mr. Sakuta, let's
get on with the lesson already!</b></Default>

00:06:44.199 --> 00:06:46.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think this might
just be the first time</b></Default>

00:06:46.449 --> 00:06:48.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've ever seen Yamada
being so motivated.</b></Default>

00:06:48.910 --> 00:06:50.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So stupid.</b></Default>

00:06:51.579 --> 00:06:53.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}This is all{\i0}
{\i1}exactly like the dream.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:06:54.500 --> 00:06:57.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}So this must be the rumor</b></Default>

00:06:58.250 --> 00:06:59.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[unlocking door]</b></Default>

00:07:00.079 --> 00:07:02.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, I'm home, Natsuno.</b></Default>

00:07:02.199 --> 00:07:03.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

00:07:06.329 --> 00:07:08.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>SANTA</b></Default>

00:07:08.410 --> 00:07:10.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, Azusagawa here.</b></Default>

00:07:11.910 --> 00:07:14.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would this happen
to be Touko Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:07:14.199 --> 00:07:17.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] {\i1}If you memorized{\i0}
{\i1}my number in that one instant</b></Default>

00:07:17.250 --> 00:07:18.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}you're{\i0}
{\i1}surprisingly intelligent.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:19.000 --> 00:07:20.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get that a lot.</b></Default>

00:07:20.290 --> 00:07:22.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}And yet you're so stupid.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:22.199 --> 00:07:25.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}If I didn't get a call back{\i0}
{\i1}after trying multiple times</b></Default>

00:07:25.120 --> 00:07:27.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}don't you think{\i0}
{\i1}I'd assume you're avoiding me?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:27.500 --> 00:07:28.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad you called.</b></Default>

00:07:28.620 --> 00:07:30.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's something
I have to ask you.</b></Default>

00:07:30.579 --> 00:07:33.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}How to become Santa Claus{\i0}
{\i1}is a secret.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:33.250 --> 00:07:34.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can we meet again?</b></Default>

00:07:34.500 --> 00:07:37.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}It is the first day{\i0}
{\i1}of December, you know.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:37.120 --> 00:07:39.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Santa Claus{\i0}
{\i1}is a very busy woman.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:39.449 --> 00:07:41.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you please
just fit it in your schedule?</b></Default>

00:07:42.079 --> 00:07:45.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Then tomorrow, after fourth{\i0}
{\i1}period, at the front gate.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:45.500 --> 00:07:47.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, well</b></Default>

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}What, you're busy tomorrow?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:50.250 --> 00:07:51.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's my girlfriend's birthday.</b></Default>

00:07:52.829 --> 00:07:53.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Oh.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:57.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Then I refuse to see you{\i0}
{\i1}on any day other than tomorrow.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:07:57.410 --> 00:07:58.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Touko hangs up]</b></Default>

00:07:58.790 --> 00:08:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[sighs]
-[meows]</b></Default>

00:08:00.870 --> 00:08:02.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] I understand.</b></Default>

00:08:02.199 --> 00:08:03.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 2ND</b></Default>

00:08:03.199 --> 00:08:04.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're meeting Kirishima today</b></Default>

00:08:04.910 --> 00:08:06.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you're canceling
your date with me.</b></Default>

00:08:07.040 --> 00:08:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

00:08:08.370 --> 00:08:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you acting dissatisfied</b></Default>

00:08:10.079 --> 00:08:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you're the one
who changed plans?</b></Default>

00:08:12.079 --> 00:08:14.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was really
looking forward to this.</b></Default>

00:08:14.120 --> 00:08:15.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nuh-uh. That's my line.</b></Default>

00:08:15.829 --> 00:08:17.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[car accelerating]</b></Default>

00:08:17.620 --> 00:08:20.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai, I'd like you to show
some more disappointment.</b></Default>

00:08:20.500 --> 00:08:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course I'm disappointed.</b></Default>

00:08:22.120 --> 00:08:24.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All the preparation I did
is for nothing now.</b></Default>

00:08:25.250 --> 00:08:27.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm happy just getting to spend
whatever time I can</b></Default>

00:08:27.870 --> 00:08:29.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with my beautiful Mai.</b></Default>

00:08:29.079 --> 00:08:30.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not happy about this at all.</b></Default>

00:08:31.620 --> 00:08:34.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Either way</b></Default>

00:08:34.409 --> 00:08:37.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just be grateful your girlfriend
is so understanding.</b></Default>

00:08:37.250 --> 00:08:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hard to be grateful</b></Default>

00:08:38.450 --> 00:08:41.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when I have less time to spend
with my perfect girlfriend.</b></Default>

00:08:41.500 --> 00:08:43.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then do you want me
to go along with you?</b></Default>

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, you can't!</b></Default>

00:08:51.500 --> 00:08:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] You don't have to
worry about it.</b></Default>

00:08:53.580 --> 00:08:55.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Of course
I'm gonna worry.</b></Default>

00:08:55.830 --> 00:08:58.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand that you're
concerned about me, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:08:59.039 --> 00:09:01.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all</b></Default>

00:09:01.870 --> 00:09:04.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

00:09:07.289 --> 00:09:09.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you not feel uneasy?</b></Default>

00:09:09.620 --> 00:09:11.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got you around</b></Default>

00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:17.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, uh, Mai?</b></Default>

00:09:17.909 --> 00:09:18.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:09:18.909 --> 00:09:21.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you stop
by the next convenience store?</b></Default>

00:09:21.500 --> 00:09:22.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What for?</b></Default>

00:09:22.500 --> 00:09:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want to hug you.</b></Default>

00:09:24.080 --> 00:09:25.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then no.</b></Default>

00:09:25.159 --> 00:09:26.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

00:09:28.539 --> 00:09:31.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, for second period</b></Default>

00:09:31.159 --> 00:09:33.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you have enough lectures
attended, right?</b></Default>

00:09:33.659 --> 00:09:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Why do you ask?</b></Default>

00:09:35.580 --> 00:09:37.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indicator clicking]</b></Default>

00:09:37.250 --> 00:09:38.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Mai.</b></Default>

00:09:38.450 --> 00:09:40.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are we playing hooky?</b></Default>

00:09:40.789 --> 00:09:42.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Today is my birthday</b></Default>

00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so we can be tardy.</b></Default>

00:09:45.039 --> 00:09:46.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:09:48.039 --> 00:09:50.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Uh, Mai</b></Default>

00:09:51.159 --> 00:09:52.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Follow me and find out.</b></Default>

00:09:54.250 --> 00:09:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Uh...
-I turn 20 today</b></Default>

00:09:56.409 --> 00:09:58.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so don't you think
I deserve a special gift</b></Default>

00:09:58.659 --> 00:10:00.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from my loving boyfriend?</b></Default>

00:10:00.789 --> 00:10:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, definitely.</b></Default>

00:10:12.700 --> 00:10:13.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How's this?</b></Default>

00:10:17.370 --> 00:10:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It suits you very well.</b></Default>

00:10:19.909 --> 00:10:22.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They said they'll be eagerly
awaiting our next visit.</b></Default>

00:10:22.750 --> 00:10:25.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, the next time, we can go
buy an engagement ring for you.</b></Default>

00:10:25.950 --> 00:10:28.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I wouldn't mind
looking forward to that.</b></Default>

00:10:29.159 --> 00:10:30.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I'll see you tonight.</b></Default>

00:10:31.250 --> 00:10:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Oh, yeah. Hey, Mai.
-Hmm?</b></Default>

00:10:33.870 --> 00:10:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I forgot.</b></Default>

00:10:35.080 --> 00:10:36.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Happy birthday.</b></Default>

00:10:37.289 --> 00:10:38.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:10:38.580 --> 00:10:41.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're always so late
at saying things.</b></Default>

00:10:41.159 --> 00:10:42.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>YOKOHAMA CITY UNIVERSITY</b></Default>

00:10:42.500 --> 00:10:44.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad I withdrew
my paycheck yesterday</b></Default>

00:10:44.789 --> 00:10:46.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in preparation for the date.</b></Default>

00:10:46.289 --> 00:10:48.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mai's hand was
absolutely glimmering today.</b></Default>

00:10:49.039 --> 00:10:50.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So then</b></Default>

00:10:50.080 --> 00:10:52.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was that her b'day present
from you, Azusagawa?</b></Default>

00:10:52.539 --> 00:10:53.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, yeah.</b></Default>

00:10:53.539 --> 00:10:55.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The ring is so nice.</b></Default>

00:10:55.409 --> 00:10:58.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really wanted to give one
to Mai as a present too.</b></Default>

00:10:58.289 --> 00:11:00.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shouldn't you be
on the receiving end?</b></Default>

00:11:00.330 --> 00:11:02.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no one I want to
receive one from right now.</b></Default>

00:11:03.080 --> 00:11:06.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, by the way, if you're
curious, my birthday is--</b></Default>

00:11:06.159 --> 00:11:09.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you keep saying that stuff</b></Default>

00:11:09.370 --> 00:11:11.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Relax. I'd only say it to you.</b></Default>

00:11:11.700 --> 00:11:14.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And saying stuff like that
is why you're so popular.</b></Default>

00:11:18.950 --> 00:11:20.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's not here.</b></Default>

00:11:21.700 --> 00:11:23.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess
she wants me to wait for her.</b></Default>

00:11:23.870 --> 00:11:25.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN]
Is this some kind of joke?</b></Default>

00:11:25.750 --> 00:11:27.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not funny at all.</b></Default>

00:11:28.250 --> 00:11:29.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry to make you wait</b></Default>

00:11:30.200 --> 00:11:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:33.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:11:35.159 --> 00:11:38.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] So even Santa Claus
wears normal clothing, huh?</b></Default>

00:11:38.620 --> 00:11:40.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] With how dense you are</b></Default>

00:11:40.500 --> 00:11:42.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>doesn't your girlfriend
get disappointed?</b></Default>

00:11:42.950 --> 00:11:45.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] She occasionally
says she loves it.</b></Default>

00:11:46.700 --> 00:11:48.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you live around this area?</b></Default>

00:11:58.539 --> 00:12:00.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Mont Blanc
and Earl Grey.</b></Default>

00:12:00.500 --> 00:12:01.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:12:01.950 --> 00:12:05.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Welcome, sir. Will you be dining
as a party of one this evening?</b></Default>

00:12:06.450 --> 00:12:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. I would like a Mont Blanc
and an Earl Grey, please.</b></Default>

00:12:12.409 --> 00:12:13.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here you go.</b></Default>

00:12:14.830 --> 00:12:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't mind if I do.</b></Default>

00:12:20.830 --> 00:12:21.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mmm!</b></Default>

00:12:22.039 --> 00:12:23.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Kirishima</b></Default>

00:12:23.120 --> 00:12:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is there anything else
that you're troubled by?</b></Default>

00:12:25.580 --> 00:12:26.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Anything else"?</b></Default>

00:12:26.870 --> 00:12:28.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What could trouble me?</b></Default>

00:12:28.450 --> 00:12:30.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, things other than</b></Default>

00:12:30.159 --> 00:12:33.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how you can't eat the Mont Blanc
from here if I'm not around.</b></Default>

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:35.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your predicament here</b></Default>

00:12:35.870 --> 00:12:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's puberty syndrome, right?</b></Default>

00:12:37.830 --> 00:12:40.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no troubles
other than the inability</b></Default>

00:12:40.120 --> 00:12:42.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to eat the Mont Blanc
from this shop.</b></Default>

00:12:42.080 --> 00:12:43.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What about shopping?</b></Default>

00:12:43.370 --> 00:12:45.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can buy anything
on the internet nowadays.</b></Default>

00:12:45.789 --> 00:12:48.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I see. Then you must be
rather satisfied</b></Default>

00:12:48.250 --> 00:12:49.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the current situation.</b></Default>

00:12:49.789 --> 00:12:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't say
I'm satisfied just yet.</b></Default>

00:12:52.080 --> 00:12:53.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I could have things my way</b></Default>

00:12:53.750 --> 00:12:56.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd want tons more people
to listen to my songs.</b></Default>

00:12:56.409 --> 00:12:57.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can't you make that happen</b></Default>

00:12:57.950 --> 00:13:00.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if you stop
being an invisible person?</b></Default>

00:13:00.200 --> 00:13:02.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd argue I can do it
while staying invisible too.</b></Default>

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:06.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have any ideas
as to why you ended up this way?</b></Default>

00:13:06.250 --> 00:13:10.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I see. So you want to cure
my puberty syndrome, don't you?</b></Default>

00:13:10.789 --> 00:13:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since you're changing subjects</b></Default>

00:13:13.080 --> 00:13:16.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I take it that means
you must have an idea.</b></Default>

00:13:17.120 --> 00:13:18.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me.</b></Default>

00:13:18.330 --> 00:13:21.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Will you keep manifesting
other people's puberty syndrome?</b></Default>

00:13:21.370 --> 00:13:24.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I'm doing
is delivering my songs to them.</b></Default>

00:13:24.159 --> 00:13:26.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This song saved me
during a hard time.</b></Default>

00:13:26.370 --> 00:13:28.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel like
she's singing the feelings</b></Default>

00:13:28.450 --> 00:13:31.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm unable to express. I'm just
dying to hear more from her.</b></Default>

00:13:31.659 --> 00:13:33.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm trying to answer the voices</b></Default>

00:13:33.409 --> 00:13:35.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from everyone
who watches my videos.</b></Default>

00:13:35.539 --> 00:13:38.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the reason
why I continue singing.</b></Default>

00:13:38.250 --> 00:13:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, what's so bad
about that, huh?</b></Default>

00:13:40.750 --> 00:13:42.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Kirishima</b></Default>

00:13:42.159 --> 00:13:44.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the songs you've released
have become catalysts</b></Default>

00:13:44.620 --> 00:13:46.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for other people
receiving puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:13:46.909 --> 00:13:48.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're aware of that fact?</b></Default>

00:13:49.500 --> 00:13:52.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why you mentioned
the other day that</b></Default>

00:13:52.120 --> 00:13:55.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you gave Hirokawa the ability
to read the atmosphere.</b></Default>

00:13:55.909 --> 00:13:59.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's because you deliver
puberty syndrome through songs.</b></Default>

00:14:01.000 --> 00:14:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When will you be singing next?</b></Default>

00:14:04.580 --> 00:14:05.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:14:06.120 --> 00:14:09.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's annoying for you to keep
calling me over and over again</b></Default>

00:14:09.789 --> 00:14:12.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'll make an exception
and tell you.</b></Default>

00:14:12.370 --> 00:14:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm actually in the middle of
producing a new song right now.</b></Default>

00:14:16.200 --> 00:14:19.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A Christmas song I want everyone
to hear on Christmas Eve.</b></Default>

00:14:19.289 --> 00:14:21.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be a good boy and wait for it.</b></Default>

00:14:21.289 --> 00:14:23.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I do as you say</b></Default>

00:14:23.909 --> 00:14:26.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Receiving Christmas presents
from Santa Claus</b></Default>

00:14:26.370 --> 00:14:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>makes everyone happy</b></Default>

00:14:28.289 --> 00:14:30.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you say "everyone"</b></Default>

00:14:30.539 --> 00:14:33.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that high school student
over there will benefit too?</b></Default>

00:14:33.330 --> 00:14:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If he stays on the nice list.</b></Default>

00:14:35.409 --> 00:14:36.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] That person too?</b></Default>

00:14:36.909 --> 00:14:38.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] If she stays
on the nice list.</b></Default>

00:14:39.289 --> 00:14:41.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, Mai too?</b></Default>

00:14:43.580 --> 00:14:45.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She doesn't need it, does she?</b></Default>

00:14:45.750 --> 00:14:48.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean</b></Default>

00:14:48.159 --> 00:14:51.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you perhaps dislike Mai
for some reason?</b></Default>

00:14:51.539 --> 00:14:54.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I used to hate her</b></Default>

00:14:54.200 --> 00:14:55.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it's different now?</b></Default>

00:14:55.909 --> 00:14:58.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nowadays, I see her
slightly favorably</b></Default>

00:14:58.620 --> 00:15:01.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because she's dating
a very strange boy.</b></Default>

00:15:02.830 --> 00:15:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you aren't
going to hurt Mai, are you?</b></Default>

00:15:07.039 --> 00:15:09.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is this conversation about?</b></Default>

00:15:11.039 --> 00:15:12.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:15:14.289 --> 00:15:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's about how deeply in love
with Mai I am, of course.</b></Default>

00:15:18.080 --> 00:15:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOUKO] Goodness.</b></Default>

00:15:19.159 --> 00:15:21.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She really does have
strange taste in guys.</b></Default>

00:15:23.539 --> 00:15:25.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I ask you one last thing?</b></Default>

00:15:25.950 --> 00:15:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is?</b></Default>

00:15:27.080 --> 00:15:28.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just curious.</b></Default>

00:15:28.580 --> 00:15:31.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How does it feel for so many
people to listen to your songs?</b></Default>

00:15:31.909 --> 00:15:33.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's nothing else
in the world</b></Default>

00:15:33.700 --> 00:15:35.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that feels quite so amazing.</b></Default>

00:15:35.950 --> 00:15:37.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I can't stop.</b></Default>

00:15:40.500 --> 00:15:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for the treat today.</b></Default>

00:15:43.409 --> 00:15:44.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you.</b></Default>

00:15:50.789 --> 00:15:54.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess I'll buy some more
Mont Blanc to go and head home.</b></Default>

00:15:54.750 --> 00:15:56.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens, closes]</b></Default>

00:15:56.120 --> 00:15:57.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I'm back.</b></Default>

00:15:57.500 --> 00:15:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ pop song playing on TV]</b></Default>

00:16:03.330 --> 00:16:04.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Welcome home, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:16:04.870 --> 00:16:06.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, it's good to be home, Mai.</b></Default>

00:16:07.950 --> 00:16:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Welcome back</b></Default>

00:16:10.039 --> 00:16:11.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Yeah.</b></Default>

00:16:14.080 --> 00:16:16.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this Touko Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:16:16.870 --> 00:16:17.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Yep.</b></Default>

00:16:25.000 --> 00:16:26.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[song ends]</b></Default>

00:16:26.870 --> 00:16:29.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what's Zukki
doing here today?</b></Default>

00:16:29.659 --> 00:16:31.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I came here to eat some cake.</b></Default>

00:16:31.370 --> 00:16:32.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think the correct answer is</b></Default>

00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"I came to celebrate
Mai's birthday."</b></Default>

00:16:34.950 --> 00:16:37.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We all sang "Happy Birthday"
to her already.</b></Default>

00:16:37.750 --> 00:16:39.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even Kaede sang with us too.</b></Default>

00:16:40.250 --> 00:16:41.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh?</b></Default>

00:16:41.500 --> 00:16:43.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, so what if I did?</b></Default>

00:16:43.409 --> 00:16:45.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, what's in that box?</b></Default>

00:16:45.700 --> 00:16:49.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A bit of Mont Blanc that is best
eaten in the next 15 minutes.</b></Default>

00:16:50.289 --> 00:16:51.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] Big Brother, Mai</b></Default>

00:16:51.950 --> 00:16:53.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>thank you for all the food.</b></Default>

00:16:53.789 --> 00:16:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you guys.</b></Default>

00:16:54.789 --> 00:16:56.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm gonna escort Uzuki
back home.</b></Default>

00:16:56.580 --> 00:16:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm heading
to the convenience store.</b></Default>

00:16:58.539 --> 00:17:00.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Sure thing.
Just be careful.</b></Default>

00:17:00.580 --> 00:17:01.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door closes]</b></Default>

00:17:01.870 --> 00:17:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have I forced Kaede
to be considerate as well?</b></Default>

00:17:04.829 --> 00:17:06.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since we're alone</b></Default>

00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:07.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I don't.</b></Default>

00:17:08.039 --> 00:17:09.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aww.</b></Default>

00:17:10.410 --> 00:17:12.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's what she told you?</b></Default>

00:17:12.200 --> 00:17:14.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That she actually used to
hate me for some reason?</b></Default>

00:17:14.910 --> 00:17:15.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:17:16.000 --> 00:17:18.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you ever do something mean
to Touko Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:17:18.700 --> 00:17:21.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, of course not.
I've never even met her.</b></Default>

00:17:21.700 --> 00:17:23.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but you are
in show business</b></Default>

00:17:23.829 --> 00:17:26.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so do you think you could be
the target of one-sided envy?</b></Default>

00:17:27.000 --> 00:17:29.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe. But when you were
chatting with her</b></Default>

00:17:29.829 --> 00:17:31.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it didn't seem like
she had any intention</b></Default>

00:17:32.039 --> 00:17:33.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of harming me directly, did it?</b></Default>

00:17:33.789 --> 00:17:36.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, I didn't sense danger
or anything of that nature</b></Default>

00:17:36.539 --> 00:17:37.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>coming from her.</b></Default>

00:17:37.539 --> 00:17:39.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am curious
about the Christmas song</b></Default>

00:17:39.500 --> 00:17:41.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she wants people to listen to
on Christmas Eve.</b></Default>

00:17:43.160 --> 00:17:44.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>By the way, Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:17:44.619 --> 00:17:45.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:17:45.660 --> 00:17:48.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Leave your schedule open
for the 24th and 25th, okay?</b></Default>

00:17:48.950 --> 00:17:52.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've already left it open to
spend those days with you, Mai.</b></Default>

00:17:52.079 --> 00:17:54.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good. I'll stay with you
the whole time</b></Default>

00:17:54.289 --> 00:17:56.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during those two days
so you can feel at ease.</b></Default>

00:17:56.660 --> 00:17:57.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seriously?</b></Default>

00:17:57.700 --> 00:18:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hakone has lovely hot springs.
We can go and relax.</b></Default>

00:18:01.329 --> 00:18:03.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can think of it
as a Christmas present</b></Default>

00:18:03.539 --> 00:18:04.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from me to you.</b></Default>

00:18:04.829 --> 00:18:06.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sound good?</b></Default>

00:18:06.160 --> 00:18:07.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:18:07.200 --> 00:18:09.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Yahoo!</b></Default>

00:18:11.579 --> 00:18:13.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct chatter]</b></Default>

00:18:14.079 --> 00:18:15.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SANTA] Merry Christmas.</b></Default>

00:18:16.789 --> 00:18:18.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Merry Christmas.</b></Default>

00:18:19.500 --> 00:18:20.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Merry Christmas.</b></Default>

00:18:21.250 --> 00:18:23.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] Sorry to make you wait.</b></Default>

00:18:23.119 --> 00:18:25.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you think
about my outfit?</b></Default>

00:18:25.160 --> 00:18:26.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Hmm.</b></Default>

00:18:26.539 --> 00:18:28.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks pretty cold.</b></Default>

00:18:28.119 --> 00:18:30.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Jeez, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:18:30.950 --> 00:18:32.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles] But still, though</b></Default>

00:18:32.539 --> 00:18:36.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm really happy I can spend
Christmas Eve with you.</b></Default>

00:18:37.579 --> 00:18:40.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>GOKURAKUJI</b></Default>

00:18:42.289 --> 00:18:43.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:18:43.750 --> 00:18:45.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you still remember
our promise?</b></Default>

00:18:45.750 --> 00:18:46.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Hmm?</b></Default>

00:18:46.789 --> 00:18:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You promised me
you wouldn't try</b></Default>

00:18:48.539 --> 00:18:50.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to cure my puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:18:50.539 --> 00:18:51.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I do.</b></Default>

00:18:51.660 --> 00:18:54.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I know you can be a liar
sometimes, too, so...</b></Default>

00:18:55.539 --> 00:18:57.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}♪ If you lie{\i0}
{\i1}and break your promise ♪{\i0}</b></Default>

00:18:57.660 --> 00:18:59.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}♪ I'll make you swallow{\i0}
{\i1}1</b></Default>

00:18:59.829 --> 00:19:01.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}♪ All in a big gulp ♪{\i0}</b></Default>

00:19:01.450 --> 00:19:02.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}♪ Pinky promise ♪{\i0}</b></Default>

00:19:03.869 --> 00:19:05.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Natsuno purring]</b></Default>

00:19:10.500 --> 00:19:12.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What the heck can it be?</b></Default>

00:19:12.910 --> 00:19:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was another dream?</b></Default>

00:19:14.869 --> 00:19:15.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 3RD</b></Default>

00:19:16.579 --> 00:19:18.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] If the dream
I had this morning</b></Default>

00:19:18.789 --> 00:19:20.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is gonna become reality
once again</b></Default>

00:19:20.829 --> 00:19:24.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that means I'd be canceling
the overnight trip with Mai</b></Default>

00:19:24.200 --> 00:19:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to go on a Christmas date
with Himeji, of all people.</b></Default>

00:19:27.700 --> 00:19:29.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You promised me
that you wouldn't try</b></Default>

00:19:29.700 --> 00:19:31.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to cure my puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:19:32.039 --> 00:19:35.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That pretty much confirms that
a new case of puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:19:35.250 --> 00:19:37.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has already manifested
inside of Himeji.</b></Default>

00:19:37.910 --> 00:19:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What a mess.
-[door opens]</b></Default>

00:19:39.700 --> 00:19:41.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KOGA] What's a mess, Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:19:41.910 --> 00:19:44.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I sort of had
a weird dream last night.</b></Default>

00:19:44.369 --> 00:19:47.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe it's like one of those
you'd find on #Dreaming.</b></Default>

00:19:47.289 --> 00:19:48.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For real?</b></Default>

00:19:48.369 --> 00:19:50.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>More people are talking
about the Dreaming tag</b></Default>

00:19:50.869 --> 00:19:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at school lately too.</b></Default>

00:19:52.079 --> 00:19:54.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess a lot of people
are buying into it.</b></Default>

00:19:54.369 --> 00:19:57.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So anyway, what's so strange
about the dream you had?</b></Default>

00:19:57.160 --> 00:19:59.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's just say
I'd be in big trouble</b></Default>

00:19:59.160 --> 00:20:00.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if it became reality.</b></Default>

00:20:00.619 --> 00:20:02.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hmm?
-[phone vibrates]</b></Default>

00:20:03.039 --> 00:20:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Sakuta. Did you
do something to Himeji?</b></Default>

00:20:06.329 --> 00:20:07.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. Nothing yet.</b></Default>

00:20:07.950 --> 00:20:09.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:20:09.329 --> 00:20:11.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What time
does your shift end today?</b></Default>

00:20:11.579 --> 00:20:12.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At 9:00.</b></Default>

00:20:12.750 --> 00:20:15.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's asking you, "Can I have
some of your time after work?"</b></Default>

00:20:15.869 --> 00:20:18.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can tell her
that won't be a problem.</b></Default>

00:20:19.289 --> 00:20:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What?
-Oh, nothing.</b></Default>

00:20:21.829 --> 00:20:24.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Himeji is
super popular with guys</b></Default>

00:20:24.539 --> 00:20:27.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'd just be careful
around her if I were you.</b></Default>

00:20:27.579 --> 00:20:29.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] {\i1}Hello and welcome</b></Default>

00:20:30.039 --> 00:20:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}This is Mai Sakurajima.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:32.450 --> 00:20:33.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I am once again in charge{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:33.869 --> 00:20:36.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}of bringing big camera store{\i0}
{\i1}announcements to all of you.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:20:37.450 --> 00:20:38.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] Guess who?</b></Default>

00:20:41.160 --> 00:20:44.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Himeji, you're someone that
pulls childish pranks too, huh?</b></Default>

00:20:44.579 --> 00:20:46.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I am still a child</b></Default>

00:20:46.950 --> 00:20:48.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm three years
younger than you.</b></Default>

00:20:48.700 --> 00:20:51.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel like most kids these days
don't like admitting</b></Default>

00:20:51.500 --> 00:20:53.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that they're
still children, though.</b></Default>

00:20:53.410 --> 00:20:56.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, what did you
call me out here for?</b></Default>

00:20:56.329 --> 00:20:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:20:57.829 --> 00:21:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you know about #Dreaming</b></Default>

00:21:00.079 --> 00:21:01.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I'm familiar with it.</b></Default>

00:21:01.950 --> 00:21:04.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I woke up from the strangest
dream this morning</b></Default>

00:21:04.750 --> 00:21:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I think
it was about Christmas Eve.</b></Default>

00:21:06.869 --> 00:21:07.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh?</b></Default>

00:21:07.869 --> 00:21:09.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For some reason</b></Default>

00:21:10.039 --> 00:21:12.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think we were on a date
or something.</b></Default>

00:21:12.500 --> 00:21:15.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. And then you and I
made a pinky promise</b></Default>

00:21:15.119 --> 00:21:17.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>inside of an Enoden train</b></Default>

00:21:17.200 --> 00:21:19.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh? Wait. Can it be
that you saw it, too?</b></Default>

00:21:19.869 --> 00:21:22.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I did.
It's likely the same dream.</b></Default>

00:21:22.700 --> 00:21:25.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's so weird. Can something
like this actually happen?</b></Default>

00:21:25.910 --> 00:21:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is one thing
that I want to confirm.</b></Default>

00:21:28.160 --> 00:21:30.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah. Is it about
my puberty syndrome?</b></Default>

00:21:30.539 --> 00:21:32.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Was that part true?</b></Default>

00:21:32.950 --> 00:21:36.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. I do indeed
have puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:21:36.200 --> 00:21:38.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What kind
of puberty syndrome is it?</b></Default>

00:21:38.539 --> 00:21:40.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's my little secret.</b></Default>

00:21:40.250 --> 00:21:41.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From when?</b></Default>

00:21:41.250 --> 00:21:43.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From the morning
after Golden Week.</b></Default>

00:21:43.750 --> 00:21:45.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did something bad
happen around then?</b></Default>

00:21:46.200 --> 00:21:47.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My heart was broken.</b></Default>

00:21:47.869 --> 00:21:51.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, I got over it quickly</b></Default>

00:21:51.500 --> 00:21:53.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I'm having fun every day now.</b></Default>

00:21:53.539 --> 00:21:56.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I know I already
told you this in the dream</b></Default>

00:21:56.160 --> 00:21:59.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:21:59.250 --> 00:22:01.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>please don't go trying to cure
my puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:22:02.000 --> 00:22:03.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like I could.
Do I look like a doctor</b></Default>

00:22:03.950 --> 00:22:05.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who could fix
such ridiculous ailments?</b></Default>

00:22:06.000 --> 00:22:07.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs] No, you don't at all.</b></Default>

00:22:07.789 --> 00:22:09.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And if you don't mind</b></Default>

00:22:09.289 --> 00:22:11.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could you keep
my puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:22:11.450 --> 00:22:13.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just a secret
between us, please?</b></Default>

00:22:13.200 --> 00:22:15.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if I told people</b></Default>

00:22:15.750 --> 00:22:17.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I want to confirm.</b></Default>

00:22:17.160 --> 00:22:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You concerned about what kind
of puberty syndrome I have?</b></Default>

00:22:21.079 --> 00:22:24.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if I was concerned</b></Default>

00:22:24.079 --> 00:22:26.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I'll say this is homework
from me to you.</b></Default>

00:22:26.700 --> 00:22:29.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please think about what kind
of puberty syndrome it is</b></Default>

00:22:29.500 --> 00:22:30.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and figure it out.</b></Default>

00:22:30.579 --> 00:22:33.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I do this homework</b></Default>

00:22:33.410 --> 00:22:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, if you guess it correctly</b></Default>

00:22:36.539 --> 00:22:38.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's something
to look forward to.</b></Default>

00:22:38.450 --> 00:22:40.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can't be
anything lewd, though.</b></Default>

00:22:40.660 --> 00:22:41.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:22:42.250 --> 00:22:44.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway</b></Default>

00:22:44.200 --> 00:22:46.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Make sure you don't forget
about the homework, okay?</b></Default>

00:22:52.500 --> 00:22:53.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:22:55.450 --> 00:22:57.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:57.619 --> 00:23:04.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF HIS STUDENT</b></Default>

00:23:56.289 --> 00:23:58.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}Oh, Sakuta</b></Default>

00:23:58.500 --> 00:23:59.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NEXT EPISODE</b></Default>
